Now I have a thorough understanding of the project conventions. Let me present the complete data model design.

---

# Maum 앱 백엔드 데이터 모델 설계

## 1. 프로젝트 구조 분석 결과

프로젝트는 초기 상태(init 커밋만 존재)이며, `.claude/` 디렉토리의 스킬/에이전트 파일만 존재합니다. 기존 Entity, Schema, Proto 파일은 없습니다. 아래 설계는 스킬 파일에서 확인한 컨벤션을 완전히 준수합니다.

**확인된 컨벤션 요약:**

| 항목 | 규칙 |
|------|------|
| Entity 위치 | `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/{도메인}/` |
| Repository 위치 | `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/{도메인}/` |
| GraphQL Schema 위치 | `graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/` |
| Proto 위치 | `protobuf/src/main/proto/{도메인}/` |
| ID 전략 | UUID (`@GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")`) |
| Enum 저장 | DB에 Int로 저장 |
| 관계 방향 | 단방향 우선 (ManyToOne) |
| Catalog 매핑 | `maum` (user, profile, call), `chat` (chat_room), `moment` (post) 등 |

---

## 2. 도메인 관계도

```
UserEntity (maum.user)
    |
    +-- 1:1 --> ProfileEntity (maum.profile)
    |
    +-- 1:N --> MatchingEntity (maum.matching) [requester / receiver]
    |
    +-- 1:N --> CallEntity (maum.call) [caller / callee]
    |
    +-- 1:N --> MessageEntity (chat.message) via ChatRoomEntity (chat.chat_room)
```

도메인 간 참조는 **EntityId(String) 직접 저장** 방식을 우선 사용합니다. JPA 관계 매핑은 같은 Catalog 내 엔티티 간에만 적용합니다.

---

## 3. JPA Entity 설계

### 3-1. UserEntity

파일 위치: `/domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/user/UserEntity.kt`

```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "user")
@EntityListeners(AuditingEntityListener::class)
class UserEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    @Column(nullable = false, unique = true)
    val phoneNumber: String,

    @Column(nullable = false, unique = true)
    val nickname: String,

    // 0: ACTIVE, 1: INACTIVE, 2: BANNED
    @Column(nullable = false)
    var status: Int = 0,

    // 0: MALE, 1: FEMALE, 2: OTHER
    @Column(nullable = false)
    val gender: Int,

    @Column(nullable = false)
    val birthYear: Int,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false)
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)")
    var deletedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,
)

enum class UserStatus(val value: Int) {
    ACTIVE(0), INACTIVE(1), BANNED(2);
    companion object {
        fun fromValue(value: Int) = entries.first { it.value == value }
    }
}

enum class Gender(val value: Int) {
    MALE(0), FEMALE(1), OTHER(2);
    companion object {
        fun fromValue(value: Int) = entries.first { it.value == value }
    }
}
```

### 3-2. ProfileEntity

파일 위치: `/domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/user/ProfileEntity.kt`

```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "profile")
@EntityListeners(AuditingEntityListener::class)
class ProfileEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    // UserEntity와 같은 catalog이므로 FK 관계 허용
    @Column(nullable = false, unique = true)
    val userId: String,

    @Column(length = 200)
    var bio: String? = null,

    // 프로필 이미지 URL 목록 (JSON 또는 별도 테이블로 확장 가능)
    @Column(length = 1000)
    var profileImageUrl: String? = null,

    // 목소리 소개 오디오 URL (음성 앱 핵심 필드)
    @Column(length = 1000)
    var voiceIntroUrl: String? = null,

    // 관심사 태그 (쉼표 구분, 또는 별도 테이블로 확장)
    @Column(length = 500)
    var interests: String? = null,

    // 0: PUBLIC, 1: FRIENDS_ONLY, 2: PRIVATE
    @Column(nullable = false)
    var visibility: Int = 0,

    @Column(nullable = false)
    var mannerScore: Double = 36.5,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false)
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)

enum class ProfileVisibility(val value: Int) {
    PUBLIC(0), FRIENDS_ONLY(1), PRIVATE(2);
    companion object {
        fun fromValue(value: Int) = entries.first { it.value == value }
    }
}
```

### 3-3. MatchingEntity

파일 위치: `/domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/matching/MatchingEntity.kt`

```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(
    catalog = "maum",
    name = "matching",
    indexes = [
        Index(name = "idx_matching_requester_id", columnList = "requester_id"),
        Index(name = "idx_matching_receiver_id", columnList = "receiver_id"),
    ]
)
@EntityListeners(AuditingEntityListener::class)
class MatchingEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    @Column(name = "requester_id", nullable = false)
    val requesterId: String,

    @Column(name = "receiver_id", nullable = false)
    val receiverId: String,

    // 0: PENDING, 1: ACCEPTED, 2: REJECTED, 3: EXPIRED, 4: CANCELLED
    @Column(nullable = false)
    var status: Int = 0,

    // 매칭 만료 시각 (PENDING 상태에서 수락/거절 시한)
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)")
    val expiresAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    // 매칭 수락/거절 시각
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)")
    var resolvedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false)
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)

enum class MatchingStatus(val value: Int) {
    PENDING(0), ACCEPTED(1), REJECTED(2), EXPIRED(3), CANCELLED(4);
    companion object {
        fun fromValue(value: Int) = entries.first { it.value == value }
    }
}
```

### 3-4. CallEntity

파일 위치: `/domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/call/CallEntity.kt`

```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(
    catalog = "maum",
    name = "call",
    indexes = [
        Index(name = "idx_call_caller_id", columnList = "caller_id"),
        Index(name = "idx_call_callee_id", columnList = "callee_id"),
        Index(name = "idx_call_matching_id", columnList = "matching_id"),
    ]
)
@EntityListeners(AuditingEntityListener::class)
class CallEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    @Column(name = "caller_id", nullable = false)
    val callerId: String,

    @Column(name = "callee_id", nullable = false)
    val calleeId: String,

    // 매칭을 통한 통화인 경우 연결, 즉시 통화는 null
    @Column(name = "matching_id")
    val matchingId: String? = null,

    // 0: RINGING, 1: IN_PROGRESS, 2: ENDED, 3: MISSED, 4: DECLINED
    @Column(nullable = false)
    var status: Int = 0,

    // 통화 시작 시각
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)")
    var startedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    // 통화 종료 시각
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)")
    var endedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    // 통화 시간(초)
    @Column(nullable = false)
    var durationSeconds: Int = 0,

    // WebRTC / 외부 통화 서비스 세션 ID
    @Column(length = 200)
    val sessionId: String? = null,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false)
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)

enum class CallStatus(val value: Int) {
    RINGING(0), IN_PROGRESS(1), ENDED(2), MISSED(3), DECLINED(4);
    companion object {
        fun fromValue(value: Int) = entries.first { it.value == value }
    }
}
```

### 3-5. ChatRoomEntity

파일 위치: `/domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/chat/ChatRoomEntity.kt`

```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "chat", name = "chat_room")
@EntityListeners(AuditingEntityListener::class)
class ChatRoomEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    // 매칭 성사 후 생성되는 1:1 채팅방
    @Column(name = "matching_id", nullable = false, unique = true)
    val matchingId: String,

    @Column(name = "user1_id", nullable = false)
    val user1Id: String,

    @Column(name = "user2_id", nullable = false)
    val user2Id: String,

    // 0: ACTIVE, 1: CLOSED
    @Column(nullable = false)
    var status: Int = 0,

    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)")
    var lastMessageAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false)
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)
```

### 3-6. MessageEntity (DynamoDB 사용 권장)

메시지는 대량 쓰기/읽기가 발생하므로 DynamoDB를 사용합니다. MySQL Entity 대신 DynamoDB 스키마 설계를 제안합니다.

파일 위치: `/domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/chat/MessageDocument.kt`

```kotlin
// DynamoDB 테이블: chat_message
// Partition Key: chatRoomId (String)
// Sort Key: createdAt#messageId (String, ISO8601 + UUID, 시간순 정렬 보장)
data class MessageDocument(
    val chatRoomId: String,          // PK
    val sortKey: String,             // SK: "2026-02-28T00:00:00.000Z#uuid"
    val messageId: String,
    val senderId: String,
    // 0: TEXT, 1: IMAGE, 2: VOICE, 3: SYSTEM
    val type: Int,
    val content: String,
    val mediaUrl: String?,           // 이미지/음성 메시지 URL
    val readAt: String?,             // 수신자 읽음 시각 (ISO8601)
    val deletedAt: String?,
    val createdAt: String,           // ISO8601
)
```

---

## 4. Repository 설계

파일 위치: `/domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/`

```kotlin
// UserRepository.kt
interface UserRepository : JpaRepository<UserEntity, String> {
    fun findByPhoneNumber(phoneNumber: String): UserEntity?
    fun findByNickname(nickname: String): UserEntity?
    fun existsByNickname(nickname: String): Boolean
}

// ProfileRepository.kt
interface ProfileRepository : JpaRepository<ProfileEntity, String> {
    fun findByUserId(userId: String): ProfileEntity?
}

// MatchingRepository.kt
interface MatchingRepository : JpaRepository<MatchingEntity, String> {
    fun findByRequesterIdAndStatus(requesterId: String, status: Int): List<MatchingEntity>
    fun findByReceiverIdAndStatus(receiverId: String, status: Int): List<MatchingEntity>
    fun findByRequesterIdAndReceiverId(requesterId: String, receiverId: String): MatchingEntity?
}

// CallRepository.kt
interface CallRepository : JpaRepository<CallEntity, String> {
    fun findByCallerIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc(callerId: String): List<CallEntity>
    fun findByCalleeIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc(calleeId: String): List<CallEntity>
    fun findByMatchingId(matchingId: String): CallEntity?
}

// ChatRoomRepository.kt
interface ChatRoomRepository : JpaRepository<ChatRoomEntity, String> {
    fun findByMatchingId(matchingId: String): ChatRoomEntity?
    fun findByUser1IdOrUser2IdOrderByLastMessageAtDesc(
        user1Id: String,
        user2Id: String,
    ): List<ChatRoomEntity>
}
```

---

## 5. GraphQL 스키마 설계

파일 위치: `/graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/`

### schema.graphqls (루트 타입 정의)

```graphql
type Query
type Mutation
type Subscription
```

### user.graphqls

```graphql
type User {
    id: ID!
    nickname: String!
    gender: String!
    birthYear: Int!
    status: String!
    profile: Profile
    createdAt: String!
}

type Profile {
    id: ID!
    userId: ID!
    bio: String
    profileImageUrl: String
    voiceIntroUrl: String
    interests: [String!]!
    visibility: String!
    mannerScore: Float!
}

type SimpleUser {
    id: ID!
    nickname: String!
    profileImageUrl: String
    mannerScore: Float!
}

input UpdateProfileInput {
    bio: String
    profileImageUrl: String
    voiceIntroUrl: String
    interests: [String!]
    visibility: String
}

extend type Query {
    me: User!
    user(userId: ID!): User
}

extend type Mutation {
    updateProfile(input: UpdateProfileInput!): Profile!
}
```

### matching.graphqls

```graphql
type Matching {
    id: ID!
    requesterId: ID!
    receiverId: ID!
    requester: SimpleUser!
    receiver: SimpleUser!
    status: MatchingStatus!
    expiresAt: String
    resolvedAt: String
    createdAt: String!
}

enum MatchingStatus {
    PENDING
    ACCEPTED
    REJECTED
    EXPIRED
    CANCELLED
}

input RequestMatchingInput {
    receiverId: ID!
}

extend type Query {
    myMatchings(status: MatchingStatus, limit: Int, offset: Int): [Matching!]!
    matching(matchingId: ID!): Matching
}

extend type Mutation {
    requestMatching(input: RequestMatchingInput!): Matching!
    acceptMatching(matchingId: ID!): Matching!
    rejectMatching(matchingId: ID!): Matching!
    cancelMatching(matchingId: ID!): Matching!
}
```

### call.graphqls

```graphql
type Call {
    id: ID!
    callerId: ID!
    calleeId: ID!
    caller: SimpleUser!
    callee: SimpleUser!
    matchingId: ID
    status: CallStatus!
    startedAt: String
    endedAt: String
    durationSeconds: Int!
    createdAt: String!
}

enum CallStatus {
    RINGING
    IN_PROGRESS
    ENDED
    MISSED
    DECLINED
}

input InitiateCallInput {
    calleeId: ID!
    matchingId: ID
}

extend type Query {
    callHistory(limit: Int, offset: Int): [Call!]!
    call(callId: ID!): Call
}

extend type Mutation {
    initiateCall(input: InitiateCallInput!): Call!
    endCall(callId: ID!): Call!
    declineCall(callId: ID!): Call!
}
```

### message.graphqls

```graphql
type ChatRoom {
    id: ID!
    matchingId: ID!
    partner: SimpleUser!
    lastMessageAt: String
    status: String!
    createdAt: String!
}

type Message {
    id: ID!
    chatRoomId: ID!
    senderId: ID!
    sender: SimpleUser!
    type: MessageType!
    content: String!
    mediaUrl: String
    readAt: String
    createdAt: String!
}

enum MessageType {
    TEXT
    IMAGE
    VOICE
    SYSTEM
}

input SendMessageInput {
    chatRoomId: ID!
    type: MessageType!
    content: String!
    mediaUrl: String
}

extend type Query {
    myChatRooms(limit: Int, offset: Int): [ChatRoom!]!
    messages(chatRoomId: ID!, limit: Int, beforeSortKey: String): [Message!]!
}

extend type Mutation {
    sendMessage(input: SendMessageInput!): Message!
    markAsRead(chatRoomId: ID!, messageId: ID!): Boolean!
}
```

